Package net.demilich.metastone.game.fibers

Utilities to run a game context where its state is managed by the native Java call stack.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    GameContextFiber
    An extension of fiber that can schedules itself on a default scheduler and can change the game context objects on its stack.
    SuspendableGameContext
    A game context that uses only FiberBehaviour and suspends itself whenever an action or mulligan is requested.
